### Pruebas de API - Order Service

@host = http://localhost:8083/api/v1/orders
@token = Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Estado del servicio (Virtual Threads Check)
GET {{host}}/status

### 2. Obtener todos los pedidos
GET {{host}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### 3. Crear un nuevo pedido (Correct implementation)
POST {{host}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderNumber": "ORD-2026-001",
  "skuCode": "KB-MECH-RGB",
  "price": 89.99,
  "quantity": 2
}

### 4. Obtener pedido por ID (Reemplazar con un UUID real)
GET {{host}}/c207549a-650f-4bdf-bd69-a20ae3ee20d6
Authorization: {{token}}

### 5. Probar validación (Precio negativo - RFC 7807)
POST {{host}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderNumber": "ORD-FAULT",
  "skuCode": "KB-MECH-RGB",
  "price": -100,
  "quantity": 1
}

### 6. Probar Producto No Encontrado (404 Propagado)
POST {{host}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderNumber": "ORD-NOTFOUND",
  "skuCode": "INVALID-SKU-999",
  "price": 10.00,
  "quantity": 1
}
